<BaseLayout title="Company – The IT Guys" description="The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc. is a Kelowna-based software and technology company founded in 2018.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Company</p>
    <h1>Built on trust. Focused on useful technology.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Founded in 2018, The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc. began by providing dependable technology support to small and medium-sized businesses in British Columbia.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div>
      <h2>From supporting technology to creating it.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="copy">
      <p>The company was built on a simple principle: technology providers should act in the best interests of the people and organizations they serve.</p>
      <p>After years of supporting business technology, our focus has expanded to software development, mobile applications, web applications, and practical technology solutions.</p>
      <p>We build software that helps people solve problems, stay connected, and enjoy life a little more.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="eyebrow">Mission</p>
      <h2>The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc. builds practical software and technology solutions that solve real-world problems.</h2>
      <p class="lede">We believe software and technology should be reliable, intuitive, and genuinely useful.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
